Description:
Sameday is a Romanian parcel carrier company providing a full range of express services and operating the largest APM network in Romania, Bulgaria and Hungary. With a strong customer-centric focus, throughout our 16 years of activity, we used each day as a lesson to learn from with great ambition, in our endeavor to achieve ever better results by using cutting-edge technology and innovation.  

As you’re reading this, we have already achieved the following:
•            Over 5000 easybox parcel lockers in Romania, Bulgaria, and in Hungary;
•            24h-48 h delivery with 97% OTD (on time delivery) rates;
•            Main logistic hubs in Bucharest area, Sibiu, Budapest and Ruse; 
•            Over 88 local agencies;
•            A fleet of electric vans, plastic usage decrease, along with many other green results;
•            The Delivery company with the most spectacular growth prize for 2018 and 2019.

With SAMEDAY easyway, our latest service dedicated to everyone (with or without contract), sending a parcel locker-to-locker is easier than ever, thanks to our extensive network of over 3900 easybox locations across the Romania. 

Sameday is the trusted partner of major brands such as eMAG, Decathlon, Fashion Days, Flanco, elefant, Carturesti, Hervis, Oriflame and many others.

As you can see, we are straightforward. Is there you would like to know in particular? Drop us a line!

International cargo trucking. 
Since 1998 we've been contributing to the business of our clients.

Our expertise:
- FTL/LTL;
- Temperature-controlled transportation;
- Oversized cargo transportation;
- Project cargo transportation;
- Liquid cargo transportation;
- Hazardous cargo transportation;
- High cargo transportation;
- Freight forwarding services;

We do 18 000 transportation every year to Europe, Russia, Kazakhstan, Central Asia, China with/under shortest transit time and high quality service guarantee.
Our fleet is 500 own trucks (Euro 5-6) including tilt trailer, refrigerated semi-trailer, tanks, special vehicles for transportation of oversized cargo (tifbet, jumbo, semi 3+5, 3+6 etc.)

R Group’s perfect reputation among customers and partners have been earned over an years. That’s why its motto is “A Carrier You Can Trust”.

O Grupo Hexpress a mais de três décadas, atua na terceirização de serviços de transportes rápidos através de motociclistas, podendo ofertar para a este escritório contábil, motoboys, mensageiros, veículos leves tais como; Fiorinos, Kombis, Vans e Vucs, sempre proporcionando excelente relação custo x benefício.
